snippet.title: Destruction AllStars - State of Play | PS5
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/destruction-allstars/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Hop into the driver's seat with this in-depth look at the car-smashing, heart-pounding, thrill-seeking world of Destruction AllStars. Coming to PlayStation 5 on February 2.
 
Active PlayStation Plus members can download Destruction AllStars at no extra charge from February 2 to April 5. Details: https://www.playstation.com/ps-plus/
